2-0.query:
SELECT MIN(t.title) AS movie_title
 FROM sampled_company_name_1 AS cn,
 sampled_keyword_1 AS k,
 sampled_movie_companies_1 AS mc,
 sampled_movie_keyword_1 AS mk,
 sampled_title_1 AS t
 WHERE cn.id = mc.company_id
 AND mc.movie_id = t.id
 AND t.id = mk.movie_id
 AND mk.keyword_id = k.id
 AND mc.movie_id = mk.movie_id
 AND cn.country_code = '@param0'
 AND k.keyword = '@param1';
